ferent hosting-provider\n- Keeps cache-folder included - only excludes all files inside the cache-folder to achieve a smaller tar-archive\n\n## [1.0.4] - 2016-01-20\n\n### Fixed\n\n- Placing the sql-file in the root of combined tar-archive\n- Excluding cache-folder to achieve smaller files\n\n## [1.0.3] - 2016-01-18\n\n### Added\n\n- Placing the sql-file in the root of combined tar-archive\n- Checking if shell-commands working\n- Excluding cache-folder to achieve smaller files\n- Adding abbility to change tar-alias for different hosting-provider\n\n## [1.0.2] - 2016-01-13\n\n### Added\n\n- Ability to define groups that can see the widget. Default is only: Administartor\n\n## [1.0.1] - 2016-01-06\n\n### Added\n\n- Include \"core-folder\" placed outside the webroot.\n\n## [1.0.0] - 2016-01-02\n\n### Added\n\n- Initial Version\n\";s:13:\"setup-options\";s:37:\"backupmodx-3.0.4-pl/setup-options.php\";s:8:\"requires\";a:2:{s:3:\"php\";s:5:\">=5.6\";s:4:\"modx\";s:5:\">=2.6\";}s:9:\"signature\";s:19:\"backupmodx-3.0.4-pl\";s:6:\"action\";s:26:\"workspace/packages/install\";s:8:\"register\";s:3:\"mgr\";s:5:\"topic\";s:47:\"/workspace/package/install/backupmodx-3.0.4-pl/\";s:10:\"targetPath\";s:18:\"{core_path}backup/\";s:7:\"cronKey\";s:12:\"3e36b103dc7a\";s:14:\"package_action\";i:1;}','BackupMODX','a:38:{s:2:\"id\";s:24:\"612ce50d46bd5e174c581432\";s:7:\"package\";s:24:\"568a8995dc532f033500d60c\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:19:\"backupmodx-3.0.4-pl\";s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"BackupMODX\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.0.4\";s:13:\"version_major\";s:1:\"3\";s:13:\"version_minor\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"version_patch\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"release\";s:2:\"pl\";s:8:\"vrelease\";s:2:\"pl\";s:14:\"vrelease_index\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"author\";s:4:\"jako\";s:11:\"description\";s:892:\"<p>The BackupMODX extra is a tiny dashboard widget. Just place the widget into your dashboard and click the \"Backup\" button whenever you need a quick backup of your site. You can select either to backup your database, files 